description: Welcome to the Macallen Building, where luxury living meets breathtaking Boston skyline city views! This generously sized one-bedroom unit offers an unparalleled urban lifestyle and stunning vistas that dazzle day and night.The open layout living room & kitchen create a seamless flow, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the evening at home. Newly renovated spa-like bathroom. Solid hardwood floors & sophisticated finishes add a touch of refinement to every corner, with ample storage throughout. The primary bedroom boasts two generous closets. Bosch in-unit laundry and kitchen appliances. One garage parking space included. You'll have access to a wealth of amenities that enhance your daily life, 24/7 concierge, beautiful common areas including outdoor heated seasonal pool, bbq grill area, media room, lounge area & a private dog walk park. Centrally located, walk in minutes to restaurants, shops, Seaport District, South End or Downtown Boston, & easy highway access.
